data.description: Completely remodeled ranch in quiet neighborhood, close to town and centrally located.  Floor plan has open concept kitchen, dining and living area with laundry down the hall. Two full bathrooms plus kitchen with huge renovations features. Most updated home in the neighborhood! New windows, doors, appliance, flooring, paint and more. Modern touches throughout with two bedrooms on the first floor, one large guest sweet on the lower level with added game room in partially finished basement. Home very well maintained from the amenities to the surfaces. Find yourself in this updated ranch with large fenced in backyard, one car garage and large trees surrounding for a little privacy. Move in ready for your next dream home!
